        <h3>Problem</h3>
            <p>In 2008 the financial situation in the United States brought about record college program enrollments. With a mission to serve the community, Bellevue College opened its doors wide and along with it came a flood of financial aid applicants struggling to complete a legacy, paper application process on time. To get started, I created a plan so our team could get a deep understanding of the problem. </p>


   
