<p>I did a comprehensive content inventory of the existing financial aid website content. Using the content inventory, we worked through the details of a new information architecture and validated which information was required and what was not. With our good understanding of the users’ scenarios and tasks, we developed page templates for every page of the website and spent at least two weeks writing and editing the information. </p>


